hopobject.body: We'd like to offer you the job healthkrat.com Mother-of-two Kourtney Kardashian is showing off the results of her hard workouts! Kardashian was spotted in Mexico enjoying a little time off with her family in February 2013. The reality TV star was spotted wearing a flattering ViX bikini. Revealing her fit beach body, Kardashian has said that she lost 44 pounds since giving birth to daughter Penelope. Kardashian is also mom to son Mason and has said that "it was harder to lose weight the second time around."
